        <item>
            <title>Hyperloop One 结束营运，超级高铁正式玩完</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/hyperloop-one-2/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hyperloop-one-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/hyperloop-one-2/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 23 Dec 2023 08:36:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hyperloop One]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超级高铁]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1211517</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">据报道，Hyperloop One 公司（前身为维珍 Hyperloop 公司）正在出售资产、裁减剩余员工，并准备在 2023 年底前关闭。 而超级高铁依然暂时未有公司能实现得到。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1211518 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM-1280x852.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM-768x511.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM-1536x1022.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-22-at-12.36.46-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hyperloop One 结束营运</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">根据彭博社报道，Hyperloop One 这家充满未来感的交通初创公司，曾承诺将以航空速度让人们在几乎没有空气的管道中穿行，但它即将迎来结局。 Hyperloop One 正在出售资产、关闭办公室并裁员，以及将于今年年底正式结束营业，届时其所有知识产权都将转移到其主要股东，杜拜主要港口运营商 DP World 手中。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Hyperloop One 自 2014 年成立以来，该公司透过创投基金和其他投资筹集了约 4.5 亿美元（约 35 亿港元）。 虽然仍有一小撮新创公司在尝试建造超级高铁，但作为最大的超级铁路公司之一的消亡，可能预视了超级高铁是不切实际。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/21/24011448/hyperloop-one-shut-down-layoff-closing-elon-musk">The Verge</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/hyperloop-one-2/life-tech/smartcity/">Hyperloop One 结束营运，超级高铁正式玩完</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
